                    <h2>
                        Thrush
                    </h2>
                    <p>

                        Thrush is a fungal infection which may affect a newborn child and mother. The infection can affect the mouth of the child causing it to feed poorly.
                        The infection can causes sore breasts and nipples in the mother making it difficult to feed the baby. Thrush can be easily diagnosed and treated.
                        Shot in Africa. ENGLISH, LIVE ACTION
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>


