                    <h2>
                        Referring a Sick Baby
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        Health workers and Midwives should refer newborns showing warning signs to higher level medical care.
                        Simple preparations and taking the appropriate steps can reduce complications during the referral. Shot in Africa, ENGLISH, LIVE ACTION.
                    </p>
